headline: Meritage Homes’ First-Time Buyer Model Meets Higher Rates as Dendur Capital Exits
summary: Meritage Homes sits at the most rate-sensitive end of the housing market. After Dendur Capital exited its stake, attention now turns to whether first-time buyer demand can withstand today’s mortgage environment.
